##Hello there
There may not be much here, but once I have some projects, I promise there will be something here!
For now, have my [GPG public key](https://ajakimiuk.com/gpg.txt), it'd be great if you got on the privacy train and encrypted your emails. The simplest way you can get encrypted email is with [ProtonMail](https://protonmail.ch), which I use.
